author: Minecraft
description:
Complete challenges, uncover treasures, and unlock powerful gear in the overgrown remnants of Three Stripes City, a dynamic world for Minecraft* inspired by adidas. Delve into mysterious structures to complete ancient athletic trials, then craft armor sets inspired by real-world adidas gear. Can you harness the city’s lost powers?

Read more: https://www.minecraft.net/article/three-stripes-city
title: Three Stripes City – adidas x Minecraft Dynamic World Trailer
